headline: Northern Trust Corporation (NTRS) Could Be a Great Choice
summary: Dividends are one of the best benefits to being a shareholder, but finding a great dividend stock is no easy task. Does Northern Trust (NTRS) have what it takes? Let's find out.

headline: Northern Trust Expands CLO Middle Office Offering for Institutional Credit Managers and Asset Owners
summary: CHICAGO, February 25, 2026--Northern Trust has expanded collateralized loan obligation (CLO) middle office services for institutional clients on the Omnium platform.
